description:
The names of God in Scripture give us unique insights into His character, nature, and relationship with us. It is through understanding these names that believers can seek spiritual fortification, strength, and safety. Prepare to deepen your faith as we navigate this incredible topic.

Watch this #short clip from the Global #Campmeeting sermon, Gods Names: Unveiling Their Purpose and Significance in Our Lives, https://youtu.be/C1dPCVOLF0g as Yvonne Shelton talks about the significance and purpose of God's names in our lives.
